ind of weapons we\u0027re pulling of the streets.","docId":"121221pmt","qSentId":551,"aSentId":552},{"question":"What do you think of this debate?","answer":"There are three points that I think need to be raised.","docId":"121221pmt","qSentId":582,"aSentId":583},{"question":"Do you want to see these assault rifles just gone?","answer":"You know, I think getting rid of the assault weapons, you know, it is not a perfect bill, but we will never be able to legislate against evil.","docId":"121221pmt","qSentId":591,"aSentId":592},{"question":"What is your view?","answer":"I absolutely believe in banning those weapons.","docId":"121221pmt","qSentId":606,"aSentId":607}]